data.description: Looking for a place to call HOME? This 3/1 BLOCK HOME with Public Sewer & Water has everything you need. It makes a great investment property or starter home. House is located in Clair Mel neighborhood near Brandon. As you enter this cozy space welcomes you by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The layout maximizes comfort and  functionality with the extra space you can used as a dining room, family room or office space. Freshly painted, The AC- HVAC System was newly replaced in 2020, stainless steel appliances,  ceramic tile flooring in whole house. Since there is NO HOA nor CDDs,,, bring your toys, park your boats, your company trucks, add a fire pit, No Deed Restrictions here so enjoy stress free life.  property provides easy access to downtown, Brandon, Riverview, schools, mall, shopping, downtown and major interstates. Don't miss this opportunity to own this year in a prime location. CONTACT ME TODAY FOR A PRIVATE SHOWING.
